    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "well i mean i'm not talking about specific regions, just the general trend. it seems like every time these programs get bigger, more people just stop looking for work because the math doesn't make sense to work. can u find some data or studies that back that up? like specifically how much the benefits act as a disincentive.",
